 lonci,

733
00:28:13,620 --> 00:28:15,940
 luk,

734
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:16,700
 dinje,

735
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:17,540
 meso.

736
00:28:17,540 --> 00:28:22,520
 Svoje sinovstvo bi prodali.

737
00:28:22,540 --> 00:28:23,020
 za to.

738
00:28:23,020 --> 00:28:25,080
 Mojs je i Aron

739
00:28:25,080 --> 00:28:27,380
 su se krvlju zvojili

740
00:28:27,380 --> 00:28:28,520
 da im izbiju toj.

741
00:28:28,520 --> 00:28:30,420
 I ne može im izbiti Egipat iz njih.

742
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:32,860
 Imali smo za jest i pit

743
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:34,340
 i bili smo robovi.

744
00:28:34,340 --> 00:28:39,700
 Nemojte tako živjeti.

745
00:28:39,700 --> 00:28:41,780
 Zato pljujete u lice

746
00:28:41,780 --> 00:28:42,680
 precima

747
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:45,080
 koji su krvlju natopili ovu zemlju

748
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:46,240
 da ovdje vjera ostane

749
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:49,020
 i usmjerujete svoje potomke

750
00:28:49,020 --> 00:28:51,420
 na stramputicu vlastitog života

751
00:28:51,420 --> 00:28:52,460
 koja će ih odvest

752
00:28:52,460 --> 00:28:55,960
 u jednu novu Sodomu,

753
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:57,240
 u jedan novi Egipat.

754
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:59,400
 Ako je povijest očiteljica života,

755
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:01,280
 zar vi misli da Bog neće kazniti

756
00:29:01,280 --> 00:29:02,880
 tu oholos zapada?

757
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:08,800
 tu si pozvan biti svet.

758
00:29:08,800 --> 00:29:13,320
 Tu dopusti Bogu da bude Bog.

759
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:17,800
 I gledat ćeš čudesa.

760
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:21,860
 gledat ćeš mala i velika čuda

761
00:29:21,860 --> 00:29:24,460
 i ta jedna pojedna pobjeda

762
00:29:24,460 --> 00:29:25,740
 će budi tvoju vjeru.

763
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:34,160
 Danas se možete odlučiti za to.

764
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:37,300
 i sutra neće biti isto,

765
00:29:37,300 --> 00:29:38,920
 ili sutrašnji dan još ne postoji.

766
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:40,620
 On će ga stvoriti.

767
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,880
 hoćeš ga ti graditi s njim

768
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:45,880
 ili ćeš vođen sotonom za ruku,

769
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,860
 maštat o svoje budućnosti

770
00:29:47,860 --> 00:29:49,540
 i žalit za svojom prošlosti.

771
00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:53,680
 Jako je važna odluka ovo.

772
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:58,500
 Baš je proročki ovaj tekst

773
00:29:58,500 --> 00:29:59,240
 iz Evanđelja

774
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,880
 o neplodnoj smokvi.

775
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:07,400
 Ajmo da ovo bude ta godina.

776
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,660
 Korizma je vrijeme odluka.

777
00:30:08,660 --> 00:30:11,080
 Godina u kojoj ćemo dopustiti

778
00:30:11,080 --> 00:30:12,800
 da nas gospodin malo

779
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:14,480
 i prekopa

780
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:16,360
 i pognoji i zalije ponovo

781
00:30:16,360 --> 00:30:17,960
 da donesemo te plodove.

782
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:24,780
 Onom kralju kome služit

783
00:30:24,780 --> 00:30:26,560
 znači kraljevati.

784
00:30:26,560 --> 00:30:29,760
 Onom kralju kome služit

785
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:30,700
 znači kraljevati.

786
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:31,680
 To je ono služenje

787
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,720
 koje onda privlačno,

788
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:35,340
 koje nije sa natmurenim licem,

789
00:30:35,340 --> 00:30:36,900
 sa mrmljanjem.

790
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:40,540
 Mi imamo tako velik problem

791
00:30:40,540 --> 00:30:41,420
 sa mrmljanjem.

792
00:30:41,420 --> 00:30:42,580
 Ja ne mogu opisati

793
00:30:42,580 --> 00:30:44,420
 u koliko katoličkih obitelji

794
00:30:44,420 --> 00:30:45,500
 se ulazi

795
00:30:45,500 --> 00:30:47,380
 i samo šta ne valja.

796
00:30:47,380 --> 00:30:51,540
 Ne valja ovo, ne valja ovo.

797
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,080
 Upravo je to bilo

798
00:30:54,080 --> 00:30:55,260
 jedan od glavnih greha

799
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:57,220
 izrelaca koji su hodali u pustini.

800
00:30:57,220 --> 00:30:59,160
 Zato je li nemamo

801
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:01,340
 onu ptiću perspektivu

802
00:31:01,340 --> 00:31:02,420
 koju trebamo da dopustiti?

803
00:31:02,420 --> 00:31:03,880
 Ako se predate Bogu,

804
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:06,100
 Bog će vas uzdići kao orlove.

805
00:31:06,100 --> 00:31:08,380
 Znate što orlovi rade

806
00:31:08,380 --> 00:31:09,100
 kad je oluja?

807
00:31:09,100 --> 00:31:11,000
 Male ptice,

808
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:13,280
 kao što su golubovi,

809
00:31:13,280 --> 00:31:15,160
 počinju jako brzo

810
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,000
 mahat krilima

811
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,580
 i pošto puše jak vjetar,

812
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:21,260
 oni više ne mogu to izdržati

813
00:31:21,260 --> 00:31:23,180
 i sklone se onda u neke rupe

814
00:31:23,180 --> 00:31:24,860
 jer su išli svojim snagama.

815
00:31:24,860 --> 00:31:27,060
 A orao

816
00:31:27,060 --> 00:31:30,300
 dopušta da ga upravo ta jaka stroja

817
00:31:30,300 --> 00:31:31,800
 podigne na višu visinu,

818
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:33,900
 dođe iznad oblaka

819
00:31:33,900 --> 00:31:35,060
 i otvori krila

820
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:36,880
 i prepusti se

821
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:39,500
 da ga ta stroja nosi.

822
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:42,560
 Ove ptice kad glede orlovu lakoću

823
00:31:42,560 --> 00:31:44,180
 ne zna odakle mu to.

824
00:31:44,180 --> 00:31:45,180
 dive se orlu

825
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:47,740
 i misle da je to njegova snaga,

826
00:31:47,740 --> 00:31:48,240
 ali nije.

827
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,980
 On je samo znao

828
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:50,960
 raširit krila

829
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,800
 i pušti da ga ta struja nosi.

830
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:55,220
 E tako i vi trebate

831
00:31:55,220 --> 00:31:57,240
 neugodnosti oluje

832
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:58,180
 vašeg života

833
00:31:58,180 --> 00:32:00,060
 pretvoriti u struju

834
00:32:00,060 --> 00:32:01,160
 koja će vas donijet

835
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,120
 i dat vam jednu ptiću perspektivu,

836
00:32:03,120 --> 00:32:04,180
 jedan novi pogled

837
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:05,040
 da iza te oluje

838
00:32:05,040 --> 00:32:06,520
 dolazi sunce i bistrina.

839
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:08,920
 Zato što kaže Salomon

840
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:11,840
 da je kraljevo srce

841
00:32:11,840 --> 00:32:12,940
 u ruci jahvinoj

842
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:14,180
 kao voda tekućica.

843
00:32:14,180 --> 00:32:16,500
 Vodi ga kuda on hoće.

844
00:32:16,500 --> 00:32:19,420
 Prepoznajte Boga

845
00:32:19,420 --> 00:32:20,580
 u svakoj okolnosti

846
00:32:20,580 --> 00:32:21,400
 vašeg života.

847
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:25,660
 Prepoznajte Božje djelovanje

848
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:26,800
 olu i nek vas ono

849
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:28,200
 uzdigne vašu dušu.

850
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:32,620
 I onda ćete mnogo jasnije vidjeti

851
00:32:32,620 --> 00:32:33,760
 što i zašto je

852
00:32:33,760 --> 00:32:35,960
 se događa ovdje.

853
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,200
 Onda ćete biti

854
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,420
 proročki narod.

855
00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:41,420
 Onda će Bog s vama

856
00:32:41,420 --> 00:32:42,200
 podijeliti

857
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,660
 kao sa svetim Josipom

858
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:44,540
 šta se događa.

859
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:47,280
 Kad je Bog odlučio

860
00:32:47,280 --> 00:32:48,780
 Sodomu

861
00:32:48,780 --> 00:32:50,060
 uništit

862
00:32:50,060 --> 00:32:51,080
 on kaže

863
00:32:51,080 --> 00:32:51,960
 Bog kaže

864
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,580
 zašto da skrivam

865
00:32:53,580 --> 00:32:55,420
 od svog prijatelja Abrahama

866
00:32:55,420 --> 00:32:56,520
 što želim učiniti.

867
00:32:56,520 --> 00:32:58,900
 Bog ima potrebu

868
00:32:58,900 --> 00:33:00,560
 podijeliti sa svojim prijateljem

869
00:33:00,560 --> 00:33:02,500
 onim koji provodi vrijeme s njim

870
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:03,820
 i koji ga je naučio slušat.

871
00:33:03,820 --> 00:33:06,380
 Šta želi učiniti?

872
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:07,800
 Prorok Amos kaže

873
00:33:07,800 --> 00:33:09,780
 ništa ne čini Jahve Bog

874
00:33:09,780 --> 00:33:11,700
 a da osnove ne objavi

875
00:33:11,700 --> 00:33:13,180
 slugama svojim prorocima.

876
00:33:13,180 --> 00:33:14,100
 To ste vi.

877
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:15,940
 To je bio Mojsije Vapa

878
00:33:15,940 --> 00:33:16,500
 i u pustinji.

879
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:18,560
 O kad bi sav narod bio prorok.

880
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:20,720
 A osim kraljevske časti

881
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:23,040
 mi imamo i tu proročku čast.

882
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:24,360
 Tu proročku službu.

883
00:33:27,100 --> 00:33:29,840
 Vi ste Boži proročki narod

884
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:31,540
 kraljevsko svećenstvo.

885
00:33:31,540 --> 00:33:35,440
 Bog želi s vama podijeliti

886
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:36,360
 šta se događa

887
00:33:36,360 --> 00:33:38,140
 i u svijetu i u politici.

888
00:33:41,460 --> 00:33:43,580
 ali ako ostanemo kao golubovi

889
00:33:43,580 --> 00:33:45,040
 koji samo mrmljaju na oluju

890
00:33:45,040 --> 00:33:45,860
 koja se diže

891
00:33:45,860 --> 00:33:48,540
 neće biti nikakvog ploda

892
00:33:48,540 --> 00:33:51,820
 i sklonit ćemo se u svoja skučena skloništa

893
00:33:51,820 --> 00:33:54,740
 i grijat ćemo svoje perije

894
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:56,020
 svoj skučeni svijet.

895
00:33:56,020 --> 00:34:02,220
 Dopustite Bogu

896
00:34:02,220 --> 00:34:04,440
 da vas ponese u svoje visine.

897
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:08,700
 Kaže Izaija

898
00:34:08,700 --> 00:34:10,060
 da su Boži misli

899
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:10,920
 i Boži putevi

900
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,320
 iznad naših puteva.

901
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:16,820
 Ali u Kristu

902
00:34:16,820 --> 00:34:17,820
 se to mijenja.

903
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:19,080
 Zato sveti Pavo

904
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:20,260
 o druge korinčenima kaže

905
00:34:20,260 --> 00:34:22,560
 mi imamo Kristovu misao.

906
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:24,240
 Mi je imamo.

907
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:26,840
 Jer duhovan čovjek

908
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:27,700
 sve prosuđuje

909
00:34:27,700 --> 00:34:28,820
 kaže sveti Pavo.

910
00:34:28,820 --> 00:34:30,860
 Zar ne želite živjeti

911
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:31,560
 u toj slobodi?

912
00:34:31,560 --> 00:34:32,360
 A imate to.

913
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:35,640
 Prestanite zobat kukuruz.

914
00:34:35,640 --> 00:34:38,980
 Pozvani ste letit.

915
00:34:38,980 --> 00:34:42,400
 I ovdje ste pozvani letit.

916
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:44,300
 Kad ovdje to postignete

917
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:45,620
 Bog će vam jasno pokazati

918
00:34:45,620 --> 00:34:46,820
 šta i kako dalje.

919
00:34:50,260 --> 00:34:51,580
 ako budemo blizu

920
00:34:51,580 --> 00:34:52,440
 njegovog srca

921
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:55,940
 onda ćemo izdržati

922
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:56,920
 kad bude teško.

923
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:59,660
 navišću vam dva primjera.

924
00:34:59,660 --> 00:35:02,020
 Marta je Marija

925
00:35:02,020 --> 00:35:03,200
 i Petar i Ivan.

926
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:09,460
 Isus se nalazi u kući

927
00:35:09,460 --> 00:35:10,460
 Marta i Marije.

928
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:12,020
 Marta je zauzeta

929
00:35:12,020 --> 00:35:13,120
 oko posluživanja.

930
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,080
 nije to loši.

931
00:35:15,080 --> 00:35:16,760
 Nije Isus rekao da je loši.

932
00:35:16,760 --> 00:35:19,040
 A Marija je došla

933
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:20,940
 do njegovih nogu

934
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:22,340
 i upija

935
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:23,800
 njegovu ljubav,

936
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,740
 njegova znanja.

937
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:25,800
 Isus kaže

938
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,540
 ona je odabrala bolji dio

939
00:35:27,540 --> 00:35:28,780
 koji se neće oduzeti.

940
00:35:28,780 --> 00:35:33,360
 Imamo Petra i Ivana.

941
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:35,980
 Petar je jako hrabar.

942
00:35:35,980 --> 00:35:36,980
 Kaže

943
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:38,420
 ja ću i živo dati za tebe.

944
00:35:39,700 --> 00:35:40,800
 A on uvijek nekako ide

945
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:41,720
 ispred Isusa.

946
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:43,720
 On bi njega savjetovao.

947
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:44,780
 On zna bolje.

948
00:35:44,780 --> 00:35:45,600
 On kalkulira.

949
00:35:45,600 --> 00:35:47,020
 A šta Ivan radi

950
00:35:47,020 --> 00:35:48,440
 na posljednjoj večeri?

951
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:51,760
 On je naslonio glavu

952
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:52,780
 na Isusovo srce

953
00:35:52,780 --> 00:35:53,300
 i sluša.

954
00:35:53,300 --> 00:35:54,100
 I Petar zna

955
00:35:54,100 --> 00:35:55,440
 da je to tako.

956
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:57,000
 I zato on neće direktno pitati

957
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:57,740
 Isusa neko kaže

958
00:35:57,740 --> 00:35:58,600
 Ivan, utrkne ga.

959
00:35:58,600 --> 00:36:00,660
 Zašto?

960
00:36:00,660 --> 00:36:01,460
 On je učenik

961
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:02,140
 kojeg je Isus

962
00:36:02,140 --> 00:36:03,240
 osobito ljubio.

963
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:04,620
 Zašto ga osobito ljubio?

964
00:36:04,620 --> 00:36:05,940
 Zato je li Isus ima miljenike.

965
00:36:05,940 --> 00:36:07,200
 Pa sumlja.

966
00:36:09,020 --> 00:36:10,760
 nego on je bio s njim.

967
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:13,320
 On je mogao to osjetiti

968
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:15,360
 jer je on bio uz njega.

969
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:17,540
 I osluškivao je njegovo srce.

970
00:36:17,540 --> 00:36:18,980
 I sad imamo

971
00:36:18,980 --> 00:36:20,380
 događaj Kalvarije.

972
00:36:20,380 --> 00:36:23,000
 Ko je ispod Isusova križa?

973
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,620
 Ko je izdržao do kraja?

974
00:36:24,620 --> 00:36:28,540
 Marija i Ivan.

975
00:36:28,540 --> 00:36:30,080
 Marte nema,

976
00:36:30,080 --> 00:36:31,280
 Petar je pobjegao

977
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,480
 u strahu od sluškinje.

978
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:35,100
 Ako naučimo prebivat

979
00:36:35,100 --> 00:36:37,240
 kraj njega

980
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:38,180
 i živjeti s njim,

981
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:38,740
 biti s njim,

982
00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:39,820
 imati odnos s njim

983
00:36:39,820 --> 00:36:40,560
 kao David

984
00:36:40,560 --> 00:36:42,460
 koji je izgubio sve

985
00:36:42,460 --> 00:36:43,180
 više puta

986
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:44,280
 ali nikad nije izgubio

987
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,000
 odnos s njim

988
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,640
 i razvije cijelu lepezu

989
00:36:46,640 --> 00:36:47,920
 osjećaja prema Bogu

990
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,120
 što čitamo u psalmima,

991
00:36:49,120 --> 00:36:55,780
 onda ćemo izdržati

992
00:36:55,780 --> 00:36:56,800
 i onda kad dođe kušnja.

993
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:57,360
 I znate šta?

994
00:36:59,100 --> 00:37:00,360
 Ni Marija, Magdalena,

995
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:02,100
 ni Ivan apostol

996
00:37:02,100 --> 00:37:02,840
 nisu umrli

997
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,920
 mučeničkom smrću.

998
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:05,400
 Svi apostoli jesu,

999
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:08,040
 ali njih dvoje nisu.

1000
00:37:08,040 --> 00:37:09,060
 Zašto?

1001
00:37:09,060 --> 00:37:11,100
 Pa nije bilo potrebno.

1002
00:37:11,100 --> 00:37:12,420
 Oni su već tad bili spremni

1003
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:13,120
 umret za njega.

1004
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:14,880
 Oni su došli tamo do kraja.

1005
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:16,140
 Unatoč rimskoj vojsci,

1006
00:37:16,140 --> 00:37:18,020
 unatoč velikim svećenicima.

1007
00:37:18,580 --> 00:37:18,920
 Zašto?

1008
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:20,460
 Zato je li ih je ljubav

1009
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:21,380
 motivirala.

1010
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:24,840
 Mi moramo doći od toga

1011
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:25,800
 da nam ljubav

1012
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:28,540
 postane motiv našeg djelovanja,

1013
00:37:28,540 --> 00:37:30,980
 a to ne možemo odlučiti,

1014
00:37:30,980 --> 00:37:33,940
 nego to možemo upiti

1015
00:37:33,940 --> 00:37:35,460
 izdruženja s njim,

1016
00:37:35,460 --> 00:37:38,020
 izboravka s njim.

1017
00:37:38,020 --> 00:37:39,680
 E to je dublje predanje.

1018
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:41,920
 Nije to neka velika filozofija.

1019
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:43,620
 To je teologija koljena,

1020
00:37:43,620 --> 00:37:46,440
 koja se uči na koljenima pred njim.

1021
00:37:48,580 --> 00:37:53,200
 Završit ću sa

1022
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:55,800
 jednom objavom

1023
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,780
 koja je jako aktualna,

1024
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:58,100
 ali riječ o križnom putu,

1025
00:37:58,100 --> 00:37:59,740
 koje Isus dao svoj službenici

1026
00:37:59,740 --> 00:38:01,200
 sveto Jozefi Menendez.

1027
00:38:01,200 --> 00:38:03,960
 Ona je inače bila ponizna časna sestra

1028
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:05,340
 koja je

1029
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:07,960
 ponizna časna sestra

1030
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:09,800
 koja je cijeli svoj vijek

1031
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:11,560
 u samostalnu provela u svincu.

1032
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:13,460
 I niko od njenih sestara

1033
00:38:13,460 --> 00:38:15,400
 nije znao da ona ima mistične objave,

1034
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,700
 osim njenog duhovnika,

1035
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:18,260
 koji je naredio da to

1036
00:38:18,260 --> 00:38:19,100
 naredio,

1037
00:38:19,100 --> 00:38:20,600
 baš izrečito naredio

1038
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:22,640
 da pod poslušnost mora to napisat.

1039
00:38:22,640 --> 00:38:25,200
 I nakon smrti je to objavljeno njen.

1040
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:27,420
 I ona govori

1041
00:38:27,420 --> 00:38:30,060
 baš o ovom čeg smo se dotakli

1042
00:38:30,060 --> 00:38:31,020
 na svetoj misi,

1043
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:33,840
 vjernicima koji su tu prisutni,

1044
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:34,560
 koji dolazi.

1045
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:38,380
 i kroz meditaciju križnog puta

1046
00:38:38,380 --> 00:38:42,300
 ona govori o petoj posta

1047
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:43,540
 i o Šimunu Cirencu.

1048
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:46,640
 Takvi smo mnogi.

1049
00:38:46,640 --> 00:38:49,300
 Kaže, Šimun je

1050
00:38:49,300 --> 00:38:50,100
 unajmljen.

1051
00:38:50,100 --> 00:38:51,500
 Što znači

1052
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:53,220
 da se nada nekakvu

1053
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:55,420
 interesu od rada na koje je prisiljen.

1054
00:38:55,940 --> 00:38:57,160
 Tako i mi često gledamo.

1055
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:59,500
 Dao sam se Bogu,

1056
00:38:59,500 --> 00:39:00,520
 počeo sam postiti,

1057
00:39:00,520 --> 00:39:00,900
 moliti,

1058
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:02,360
 sve nešto otišlo gore.

1059
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:05,020
 Pa nije otišlo gore,

1060
00:39:05,020 --> 00:39:05,940
 nego je tvoje srce,

1061
00:39:05,940 --> 00:39:07,600
 tvoji motivi su sad na kušnji.

1062
00:39:09,180 --> 00:39:10,980
 Bog ne želi da ti budeš unajmljen

1063
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:12,100
 koji zbog dobitka,

1064
00:39:12,100 --> 00:39:14,980
 nekog jeftinog dobitka

1065
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:16,740
 koji ćeš i tako jednog dana izgubiti,

1066
00:39:16,740 --> 00:39:17,900
 dolaziš k njemu.

1067
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:19,520
 On će ti sve to i nadodati,

1068
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:21,120
 ali nađi njega najprije.

1069
00:39:21,120 --> 00:39:23,020
 Kaže,

1070
00:39:23,020 --> 00:39:24,680
 tako je sa mnogim dušama

1071
00:39:24,680 --> 00:39:25,940
 koji idu za mnom.

1072
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:30,100
 One nedvojbeno prihvaćaju

1073
00:39:30,100 --> 00:39:32,780
 pomagati mi nositi križ,

1074
00:39:32,780 --> 00:39:36,180
 ali brinu o svoj utjesi i odmoru.

1075
00:39:36,180 --> 00:39:38,240
 Pristaju slijediti me,

1076
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:40,760
 ali se ne odriču vlastite koristi,

1077
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:43,740
 koje za njih i dalje na prvom mjestu.

1078
00:39:43,740 --> 00:39:46,900
 Što je tebi na prvom mjestu?

1079
00:39:46,900 --> 00:39:49,480
 O čemu razmišljaš?

1080
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:51,080
 Kao ovaj svečenik

1081
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:53,400
 koji je dao mjeru od pola sata.

1082
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:55,860
 O čemu razmišljaš?

1083
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:58,840
 Ono o čemu razmišljaš najviše,

1084
00:39:58,840 --> 00:39:59,680
 to je tvoj Bog.

1085
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:10,000
 Zato joj kljevaju i puštaju da moj križ padne,

1086
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,580
 kada im njegov teret postane pretežak.

1087
00:40:12,580 --> 00:40:14,300
 Unatoč sirencu križe pada,

1088
00:40:14,300 --> 00:40:15,340
 ali tako, Isusov.

1089
00:40:15,340 --> 00:40:16,160
 Kaže,

1090
00:40:16,260 --> 00:40:18,840
 nastoje trpjeti što je moguće manje,

1091
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:21,220
 mjere svoje odricanje,

1092
00:40:21,220 --> 00:40:23,320
 izbjegavaju poniženja,

1093
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:24,500
 umor i rad,

1094
00:40:24,500 --> 00:40:26,640
 pokušavajući sebi preskrbiti,

1095
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:27,900
 barem neke užitki,

1096
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:30,900
 prihvaćajući samo ono što ne mogu izbjeći,

1097
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:33,380
 ili ono na što su strogo obvezni.

1098
00:40:33,380 --> 00:40:35,380
 Nedeljom ću odradit,

1099
00:40:35,380 --> 00:40:36,540
 post,

1100
00:40:36,540 --> 00:40:37,800
 pepelnica,

1101
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:38,740
 veliki petak,

1102
00:40:38,740 --> 00:40:40,160
 to je to.

1103
00:40:40,160 --> 00:40:42,500
 Na to smo strogo obvezni.

1104
00:40:42,500 --> 00:40:43,700
 Temi duše,

1105
00:40:43,700 --> 00:40:44,560
 kaže Isus,

1106
00:40:44,560 --> 00:40:47,660
 pomažu nositi samo malen dio križa

1107
00:40:47,660 --> 00:40:51,540
 i na taj će način jedva steć zasluge

1108
00:40:51,540 --> 00:40:53,440
 nužne za svoje spasenje.

1109
00:40:53,440 --> 00:40:58,280
 Ali u vječnosti će vidjeti koliko su zaostale na putu.

1110
00:40:58,280 --> 00:41:01,060
 Duša koja istinski ljubi,

1111
00:41:01,060 --> 00:41:03,380
 ne mjeri to što čini,

1112
00:41:03,380 --> 00:41:05,760
 niti važe koliko trpi.

1113
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:09,000
 Ona se ne cijenka ni oko rada,

1114
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:09,780
 ni oko umora.

1115
00:41:09,780 --> 00:41:12,080
 Ona ne očekuje nagradu,

1116
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:14,020
 nego slijedi sve ono za što misli

1117
00:41:14,020 --> 00:41:16,660
 da će biti najveća slava njezinom Bogu.

1118
00:41:17,660 --> 00:41:21,700
 I zato što dijeluje odano,

1119
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:23,240
 bez obzira na rezultat,

1120
00:41:23,240 --> 00:41:25,580
 ona se ne pokušava opravdavati,

1121
00:41:25,580 --> 00:41:30,040
 niti mrmljati radi svoje muke nekome.

1122
00:41:30,040 --> 00:41:32,060
 I zato što dijeluje iz ljubavi,

1123
00:41:32,060 --> 00:41:34,360
 njezini će napori i patnje

1124
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:36,400
 uvijek biti na Božju slavu.

1125
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,480
 Zato se ona ne uznemiruje

1126
00:41:38,480 --> 00:41:40,520
 i ne zabrinjava,

1127
00:41:40,520 --> 00:41:41,620
 a još manje,

1128
00:41:41,620 --> 00:41:44,840
 ako u nekoj prilici najđe na protivštine

1129
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:46,860
 progon i poniženja,

1130
00:41:46,860 --> 00:41:49,520
 jer jedini pokretač dijelovanja

1131
00:41:49,520 --> 00:41:50,360
 bila je ljubav,

1132
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:53,200
 a jedini cilj Božja ljubav.

1133
00:41:53,200 --> 00:41:57,000
 Te duše nose cijeli teret moga križa

1134
00:41:57,000 --> 00:41:58,480
 bez ikakve koristi

1135
00:41:58,480 --> 00:41:59,840
 i plaće osim ljubavi.

1136
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:02,440
 Upravo one odmaraju moje srce,

1137
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:04,240
 upravo ga one prostavljaju.

1138
00:42:04,240 --> 00:42:05,340
 I budite sigurni,

1139
00:42:05,340 --> 00:42:07,220
 ako vaše odricanje

1140
00:42:07,220 --> 00:42:08,660
 i vaše trpljenje

1141
00:42:08,660 --> 00:42:10,000
 dugo ne donese ploda

1142
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:12,180
 ili se čini da ne donosi nikakav plod,

1143
00:42:12,180 --> 00:42:14,400
 oni nisu bili ni uzaludni

1144
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:16,060
 ni bezkorisni,

1145
00:42:16,060 --> 00:42:17,900
 jer će jednoga dana

1146
00:42:17,900 --> 00:42:19,400
 žetva biti velika.

1147
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:22,060
 Ja znam da ovo zvuči

1148
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:23,200
 kao veliki zahtjev,

1149
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:24,740
 i meni osobno i svima vama.

1150
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:28,980
 Ali taj zahtjev se postiže

1151
00:42:28,980 --> 00:42:30,620
 postupno i polako,

1152
00:42:30,620 --> 00:42:33,120
 sa jednom malom odlukom.

1153
00:42:33,120 --> 00:42:34,920
 Kao i kod Jezefe Menendez.

1154
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:37,500
 Ima posao koji nije dostojanstven.

1155
00:42:37,500 --> 00:42:39,380
 Ona je sestra, časna,

1156
00:42:39,380 --> 00:42:40,980
 imala svoj poziv

1157
00:42:40,980 --> 00:42:41,920
 da služi Bogu

1158
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:43,860
 i završila kao zgajatelj svinja.

1159
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:47,480
 Ali, malo po malo,

1160
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,840
 malo po malo,

1161
00:42:48,840 --> 00:42:49,960
 malo po malo,

1162
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:50,980
 velika svetost.

1163
00:42:51,940 --> 00:42:54,480
 Nemojte, kaže Blaženja Lojzija Stepinac,

1164
00:42:54,480 --> 00:42:55,600
 kone napreduje,

1165
00:42:55,600 --> 00:42:56,540
 nazaduje.

1166
00:42:56,540 --> 00:42:58,560
 Idite malim koracima

1167
00:42:58,560 --> 00:42:59,820
 i sigurno

1168
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:01,840
 prema Božjoj proslavi

1169
00:43:01,840 --> 00:43:03,400
 ovdje i sada.

1170
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:04,400
 Amen.

